#: src-en/data/events_sector_stargrove.xml.append:6
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_stargrove.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"STARGROVE_HIGHWAYMAN_INITIAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/text"
msgstr "Purple Beard recognizes the Highwayman."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_stargrove.xml.append:12
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_stargrove.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_STARGROVE_EXIT_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Purple Beard groans as he sees the Highwayman. He pauses and then speaks, as slowly as ever. \"Oh, it's you... I see you decided to make this hellish place your home...\" He glares at the other pirate.\n"
"        \n"
"    The Highwayman's smile turns into huge grin. \"Ah, if it isn't the legendary pirate, Mister Purple Beard the Dreadful? To what do I owe the pleasure?\" You can't tell if the Highwayman's tone is mocking or sincere.\n"
"\n"
"    Purple Beard just sighs. \"If you know of the legends then you should be well aware that I don't quite enjoy small talk... We fight now, or else I will let everyone know what made you have to change your ship's paint color...\" His eyes narrow as the dread pirate stares at the other dead in their eyes.\n"
"\n"
"    The Highwayman's grin dissolves slowly, replaced by an intense look of hatred. \"...Heh. Now i know why your kid left.\" The enemy's weapons power on. A fight is inevitable."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_stargrove.xml.append:20
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_stargrove.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_STARGROVE_EXIT_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/choice[@req=\"cloaking\""
" and not(@lvl)]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_stargrove.xml.append:24
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_stargrove.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_STARGROVE_EXIT_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/choice[@req=\"cloaking\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."
